00454 BOOLEAN ReadInExtendedArmyGunChoicesStats(STR fileName)
00455 {

00457       UINT32            uiBytesRead;
00458       UINT32            uiFSize;

00464       DebugMsg(TOPIC_JA2, DBG_LEVEL_3, "Loading EnemyGunChoicess.xml" );
00465 
00466       // Open extendedarmygunchoices file
00467       hFile = FileOpen( fileName, FILE_ACCESS_READ, FALSE );
00468       if ( !hFile )
00469             return( FALSE );
00470       
00471       uiFSize = FileGetSize(hFile);
00472       lpcBuffer = (CHAR8 *) MemAlloc(uiFSize+1);
00473 
00474       //Read in block
00475       if ( !FileRead( hFile, lpcBuffer, uiFSize, &uiBytesRead ) )
00476       {
00477             MemFree(lpcBuffer);
00478             return( FALSE );
00479       }
00480 
00481       lpcBuffer[uiFSize] = 0; //add a null terminator
00482 
00483       FileClose( hFile );
00484 
00485       
00486       XML_SetElementHandler(parser, extendedarmygunchoicesStartElementHandle, extendedarmygunchoicesEndElementHandle);
00487       XML_SetCharacterDataHandler(parser, extendedarmygunchoicesCharacterDataHandle);
00488 
00489       
00490       memset(&pData,0,sizeof(pData));
00491       pData.curArray = gExtendedArmyGunChoices;
00492       pData.maxArraySize = ARMY_GUN_LEVELS; 
00493       
00494       XML_SetUserData(parser, &pData);
00495 
00496 
00497     if(!XML_Parse(parser, lpcBuffer, uiFSize, TRUE))
00498       {
00499             CHAR8 errorBuf[511];
00500 
00501             sprintf(errorBuf, "XML Parser Error in EnemyGunChoicess.xml: %s at line %d", XML_ErrorString(XML_GetErrorCode(parser)), XML_GetCurrentLineNumber(parser));
00502             LiveMessage(errorBuf);
00503 
00504             MemFree(lpcBuffer);
00505             return FALSE;
00506       }
00507 
00508       MemFree(lpcBuffer);
00509 
00510 
00511       XML_ParserFree(parser);
00512 
00513
